            "descriptionRaw": "<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>\nPerforms up to 4 attacks using Wind Spirits, dealing <color=#80FFD7FF>Anemo DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina and deals <color=#80FFD7FF>AoE Anemo DMG</color> after a short casting time.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>\nCalling upon the power of her Wind Spirits, Sucrose plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Deals <color=#80FFD7FF>AoE Anemo DMG</color> upon impact with the ground.",
            "name": "Wind Spirit Creation"
        },
