            "descriptionRaw": "Sucrose hurls an unstable concoction that creates a Large Wind Spirit.\nWhile it persists, the Large Wind Spirit will continuously pull in surrounding opponents and objects, launch nearby opponents, and deal <color=#80FFD7FF>Anemo DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Elemental Absorption</color>\nIf the Wind Spirit comes into contact with <color=#80C0FFFF>Hydro</color>/<color=#FF9999FF>Pyro</color>/<color=#99FFFFFF>Cryo</color>/<color=#FFACFFFF>Electro</color> energy, it will deal additional elemental DMG of that type.\nElemental Absorption may only occur once per use.\n\n<i>Sucrose used to give names to her volatile Anemo Hypostases, but their line of heirs quickly grew to surpass Baron Bunny the 893rd.</i>",
            "name": "Forbidden Creation - Isomer 75 / Type II"
        },
